headline: TE Connectivity (TEL): Assessing Valuation After Industrial Growth and Anticipated Earnings Acceleration
summary: TE Connectivity (TEL) just caught investors attention after its Industrial Solutions segment helped drive a 3% plus pop in the stock, as markets look ahead to a sharp jump in upcoming quarterly earnings. See our latest analysis for TE Connectivity. That industrial strength story is playing out against a powerful backdrop, with the share price at $230.16 after a recent pullback, but still supported by a strong year to date share price return and a standout multi year total shareholder return...
